      "question": "<p>Let A be a finite set of size n. The number of elements in the power set of $A\\times A$ is:</p>\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:upper-alpha\">\n<li>$2^{2^n}$</li>\n<li>$2^{n^2}$</li>\n<li>$\\left(2^n\\right)^2$</li>\n<li>$\\left(2^2\\right)^n$</li>\n<li>None of the above</li>\n</ol>",
